reviews.description: Very informative, patient and understanding! Dr. Dumi was so thourough, took me early, stayed late with me, explaining everything. She was gentle and kind as I am someone with a lot of dental anxiety. I would absolutely recommend her as a dentist!

My experience with Dr. Dumi was great. She really took the time to explain things to me and came up with a plan that suited me and my insurance. 

I also really liked that it was a smaller clinic. The atmosphere was calm and quiet, and never felt rushed like some dental offices do.
Dr Dumi was patient, thorough, and made me feel comfortable. She explained every part of the examination to me and made me feel aware and empowered to make educated decisions about my oral hygiene.

I'm very happy that I found Albloor Dental using Opencare.  My first appointment couldn't have gone better.  The office was recently renovated, new equipment, clean, and Dr Dumi and the staff provide excellent care!

Dr.Dumi was thorough, kind, and very professional. The office was clean and modern. The best part in my opinion was the level of transparency and lack of pushing for unnecessary procedures. I personally enjoy the level of information given with the use of tools and pictures, which empowers me to take care of my teeth in a better way. I highly recommend this dentist!
Friendly, helpful, and knowledgeable dentist. Teeth are well-cleaned and repaired. Would recommend.

I am so glad I chose Dr. Valbona Dumi from open care. I really appreciated how patient and thorough she was. She explained what she was doing and ensured I wasn't in pain. I wouldn't normally say that going to the dentist is an enjoyable experience, but Dr. Dumi somehow made it one. It was very clear that she loves her profession and that shows in the way she speaks to her patients. I highly recommend her!

clinic.name: Albloor Dental
clinic.description:
Our Dental Practice
We understand that scheduling dental appointments can be challenging, so we offer evening and weekend appointments by request for your convenience.

We do accept CDCP insurance at our office, though not through Open Care. Unfortunately, we do not currently accept other government insurances.

If you have any questions about insurance or scheduling, feel free to reach out to our team. We're here to assist you with your dental care needs.
